<section id="page-profile" class="page-profile">
<div class="container">
  <header class="section-header">
  <h2 class="section-title">Personal Profile</h2>
  <div class="spacer"></div>
  <p class="section-subtitle">Entrepreneurial Web Developer and Founder, currently in Berlin</p>
  </header>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <div class="profile">
        <%= image_tag 'profile-photo.png', alt: 'profile' %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9">
      <p>Originally from London, UK, I have lived in the South of France, Barcelona and for the last 5 years settled in Berlin.</p>

      <p>My last startup was 1000jobboersen.de which at one point reached over 150 employees and is still going now long after I left and recently merged with softgarden.de. I'm currently working on a new startup called Gohiring. When I'm not doing that, I'm <a href="http://blog.mattbeedle.name">blogging</a>, hacking on <a href="https://github.com/mattbeedle/capsule_crm">open</a> <a href="https://github.com/mattbeedle/usda-nutrient-database">source</a>, building new products (like <a href="http://www.salesflip.com">SalesFlip</a> and <a href="http://vegan.io">Vegan.io</a>) and learning new things.</p>

      <p>I'm proficient in Java, PHP, Ruby and Javascript (Ruby and Javascript preferred of course, please don't ask me to do PHP). I also have knowledge of C, Python, IO, Scala and Go. I'm fairly active in open source. You can check out my code on <a href="http://github.com/mattbeedle">GitHub</a> and my open source report card <a href="http://osrc.dfm.io/mattbeedle">here</a>.</p>

      <p>For a more detailed work history my <a href="http://linkedin.com/in/mattbeedle">LinkedIn profile</a> has all the information you need.</p>

      <p>I'm always interested in helping early stage startups get their product to launch and build a great development team, so if you need some help there, please <a href="#page-contact">give me a shout.</a>. I'm also extremely interested in distributed, self managed teams, using real time commuication tools and reporting.</p>

      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</section><!-- profile ends -->
